by here, and who was sitting beside him but Howard!! He surely is acting the part of a yellow dog - Enid dear please do not take this wrong I want you to know the facts, good or bad, and not ride them from your own letter judgement. Keep your eyes open and don't let the need for a mate make you feel this boy is necessarily the right one. 
He is playing upon your feelings and is not willing to do anything that is hard for himself. He is enlarging at home upon the hard place he is in due to the operation which was 

